headline: The Kraft Heinz Surprise: Outshining Defensive Packaged Foods Over Next 5 Years
summary: Kraft Heinz has significantly reduced its net debt from $31B in 2018 to $18.5B, while increasing operating cash flow. See why I rate KHC stock as a buy.
